Your father will never forgive you.
But you can't stay with us.

06:17.400 --> 06:21.598
I can't go back home, grandmother.

06:24.280 --> 06:26.077
Marium, a sister of your mother,

06:26.520 --> 06:29.637
is the wife
of the Somali ambassador in London.

06:30.080 --> 06:34.198
She is looking for a maid.

06:35.680 --> 06:39.070
It's Allah's will that you move on.

06:39.520 --> 06:42.796
There will be war in Somalia.
In Europe you are safe.

06:43.240 --> 06:45.515
Don't come back.

07:05.960 --> 07:09.270
They will try to change you there.

07:10.440 --> 07:13.477
Never forget where you come from.

07:17.440 --> 07:19.317
Here is your passport.

07:20.920 --> 07:25.152
It tells people who you are.
Without it you are no one.

07:29.080 --> 07:32.993
May Allah protect you, Afyareh.

07:33.440 --> 07:34.998
Go in peace.

13:19.360 --> 13:21.191
There is a Coup d'Etat in Somalia!
The president is deposed.

13:21.640 --> 13:24.837
The embassy staff has been recalled!
Waris, pack your belongings!

13:25.280 --> 13:27.430
I can't go back!

